text: Aptrakovo () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Aptrakovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 312 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Meleuz. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Aptrakovo
